name: Svdden Death
description: '''Daniel James "Danny" Howland''' (born June 29, 1993), better known by his alias '''Svdden Death''' (stylized in [[all caps]]), is a [[Los Angeles]] [[Disc jockey|DJ]] and [[Music Producer|producer]] from [[San Jose, California]]. He is known for his song "[[Sell Out (Marshmello and Svdden Death song)|Sell Out]]", a collaboration with American [[Multi-Platinum|multi-platinum]] artist [[Marshmello]] that peaked on [[Billboard (magazine)|''Billboard's'']] [[Dance/Electronic Songs|Hot Dance/Electronic Songs]] at the No. 36 position in early 2019. Howland makes high-energy music that falls into the genre of [[dubstep]] and [[Riddim (genre)|riddim]].
